# Ã„lplermagronen
## Ingredients
Onion 2
Garlic clove  2
Bacon
Waxy potatoes 300g
Elbow macaroni  200g
Cheese, grated  250g
Stock   5 dl
Cream   2 dl
Pepper, nutmeg

## Methods:
1. Fry bacon, garlics and onions until golden brown
2. Bring stock and milk to a boil with cubed potatoes
3. Add macaroni
4. Reduced heat, cook until al-dente
5. Stirr cheese in

## Note
- Serve with Apple sauce
- Stock and cream can be replace by milk with a bouillon cube
